programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un sospechoso fugitivo provoca a los policias generando una persecución en medio del tráfico. Imágenes de un circuito cerrado de televisón deja ver un apuñalamiento ayudando a la policía a encontrar al agresor vicioso. Los policías rastrean a un sujeto en el apartamento de un desconocido, este no coopera.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Los policias aprenden por las malas que ni un taser puede acabar con algunos sospechosos. Los coches de la patrulla se acercan a una pareja en una camioneta oscura. La policía arresta a uno de los sospechosos más educados de América.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un sospechoso corre atravesando la valla del hotel para darle una noticia impactante a un empleado. Los policias se encuentran con dos hermanos en una pelea con cuchillos. Un hombre rebelde dispara su pistola BB al hijo de un vecino.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.sub-title: Yo voy a elevar mi voz
programme.desc: El nuevo jefe de la ciudad supervisa una serie de compras de drogas encubiertas. Los oficiales arrestan a un borracho hablador. Una sospechosa de abuso doméstico admite haberle pegado a su marido.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Los policias se ven obligados a electrocutar a un suicida por su propio bien. Los policias ven un rostro conocido e inician su persecución en un campo de hierba. Ninguna mentira es demasiado grande para un sospechoso que busca refugio en un hogar perdido.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Tres hombres intentan convencer a los policías de que no sabían que su vehículo había sido robado. Los oficiales responden después de que un fiestero confunde el dedo de otro invitado con el postre. Un sospechoso de abuso doméstico huye.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un grupo de sospechosos compite con un carro deportivo robado en un barrio tranquilo. Un hombre borracho tiene un cuchillo de cocina y un problema de escucha. Dos sospechosos recurrentes van a volver a la cárcel por sus últimas aventuras.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un sospechoso que conduce bajo los efectos del alcohol le recuerda a un oficial el caso de una celebridad. Un hombre desnudo golpea a un extraño en su porsche. La pataleta de una niña sacude todo el apartamento cuando su mamá le quita Facebook.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un sospechoso corre rapidamente y hace que los oficiales lo persigan a través de un arroyo. Un adolescente buen samaritano se mete en medio de una extraña disputa doméstica. Después de que una mujer destruye su casa, le ruega a la policía que la arreste.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un hombre recibe más de lo que esperaba de su nuevo compañero de cuarto. Los policías descubren las consecuencias inesperadas de golpear una moto. Los oficiales detienen a un sospechoso sobrio que parece de otro mundo.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un sospechoso sale a cortarse el pelo y termina en la cárcel. Los agentes tratan de unir las pistas que causaron una pelea callejera desconcertante. Los policías le dan a un sospechoso la oportunidad de admitir su notorio crimen.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un sospechoso desafia a un canino policia y este le ocasiona una mordedura . Un ex prometido se convierte en una molestia del vecindario. Una retén de rutina termina en órdenes judiciales, embarazo y metanfetamina.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un policía extremadamente comprensivo le da a un sospechoso demasiadas oportunidades. Un conductor nos recuerda por qué nunca debemos prestarle nuestro auto a un amigo. Un hombre en su vehículo último modelo dice una horrible mentira a la policía.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un sospechoso utiliza técnicas de conducción extrañas para evadir a los policías. Un oficial rudo cruza un bosque antes de encontrar una grieta. La policía busca a un hombre acusado de disparar en el vecindario.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un sospechoso debe obedecer a las instrucciones de su familiar más sensato. Un imitador muerto de "The Rock" descubre una roca de crack. Los oficiales intentan sacarle la verdad a dos drogadictos conocidos.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un persona que ve monstruos se resiste a ser arrestado. Los policías se ven obligados a oficiar un combate de lucha libre conyugal. Los oficiales tratan de averiguar dónde dos automovilistas consiguieron su auto y de quién es la droga que poseen.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un peatón imprudente se lanza a correr en medio de la maleza. Las cosas van mal para un sospechoso que se encuentra en una moto robada y los helicópteros lo rastrean. Una disputa doméstica lleva a la policía a un montón de crímenes inesperados.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Subirse en el carro de un desconocido para que la llevara a su casa casi lleva a una mujer a la cárcel. Una prostituta conocida no irá a una segunda cita. Una pareja de hecho se niega a salir de casa y los agentes intervienen.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: La esposa de un hombre no puede ayudarlo a escapar de la cárcel sin importar cuánto la llame. Un ladrón intenta devolver su botín robado. Cuando se le acercan los oficiales una mujer pasa de estar dormida a estar fuera de control.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: La idea de esconderse en un último piso le falla a un hombre tras caerse del techo. Los policías detienen a un hombre con un coche roto y una decepcion amorosa . Los vecinos llaman a la policía cuando las peleas verbales interrumpen su noche.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Una vez mas una persona fastidiosa se encuentra molestando a la gente . Los oficiales se divierten con un sospechoso que siempre trae dinero en su zapato. Los policías tratan de darle sentido a un hombre que apenas es coherente.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Por beber mientras iba en bicicleta, un hombre es detenido y se marcha infeliz caminando. Una mujer no está segura de cómo terminó en un vehículo robado. Los agentes descubren a una pareja fumando metanfetamina delante de un niño.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un hombre puede pagar la pensión alimenticia, pero no puede escapar de la policía. Una mujer casi atropella a su novia. Un vago sospechoso niega que la pila de marihuana en su coche es suya.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un hombre furioso le ruega a la policía que le dispare. Una mujer borracha se enoja después de ser arrestada por agresión doméstica. Los policías descubren las mentiras mientras dan sentido a una familia disfuncional.

programme.title: Cops en Español

programme.title: Cops en Español

programme.title: Cops en Español

programme.title: Cops en Español

programme.title: Cops en Español

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un motociclista causa una persecución por las calles. Ni un carro que no prende impide que un hombre corra de la policía. Un conductor no logra evadir a la policía y se disculpa raramente con su novia.

programme.title: Cops en Español

programme.desc: La unidad K-9 responde cuando un pistolero sube a los tejados. Un intercambio de drogas sale mal cuando el traficante intenta deshacerse de su alijo. Un camionero borracho intenta jugar cuando destroza el auto de su vecino.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un retén se complica cuando un sospechoso crea una distracción momentánea. Un hombre se niega a dar su nombre real, pero los oficiales encuentran una pista. Un conductor sereno no puede ser franco.

programme.sub-title: A un paso de los cubiertos
programme.desc: Los policías intentan averiguar si un conductor que va sin rumbo , sabe que está en un vehículo robado. Un hombre que empuña un cuchillo se queja de que sus vecinos no dejan de fumar marihuana. Los oficiales encuentran a un hombre con una navaja en la garganta.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.desc: Un motociclista cuenta con la suerte de estar vivo después de estrellarse en una carretera oscura. En una parada de tráfico, los oficiales se dirigen a dos pasajeros para obtener mayor información Un conductor joven admite que su situación no es favorable cuando la policía lo detiene.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.sub-title: Armas, hachís y bocas de incendio
programme.desc: Una persecución se convierte en una inundación repentina cuando un conductor choca contra una boca de incendios. Un insolente sospechoso de violencia doméstica desvía la culpa. Los oficiales recuperan una cornucopia de contrabando de una pareja armada.

programme.title: Cops en Español
programme.sub-title: Arma de frente, rifle en la parte trasera
programme.desc: Los oficiales responden a un fatal accidente automovilístico. La policía interroga a un sospechoso por presunto robo, pero este asegura ser la verdadera víctima. Los oficiales encuentran a un hombre que dice padecer de un trastorno que lo obliga a escapar.

programme.title: Cops en Español

programme.desc: Un hombre con una orden de arresto hace todo lo posible para escapar y no ser atrapado. Las cosas se complican cuando un hombre trata de revelar todo a la policía. Un joven toma malas decisiones que lo hacen perder su hogar.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan debe juntar los vecinos de Helen para unirse y ayudar a salvar sus casas de unos desarrolladores corporativos que quieren desalojarlos.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Harry, todavía en duelo por la pérdida de su esposa, es puesto en un hogar de ancianos, pero su visión de la vida cambia cuando tiene la oportunidad de cumplir el mayor deseo de su esposa: visitar Hollywood.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: La hija de un entrenador de caballos y el hijo de un ranchero se conocen en un entrenamiento y nace una atracción entre ellos. Jonathan y Mark tienen que actuar de cupido para unirlos, a pesar de que él ya está comprometido.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Como consejeros en un campamento para jóvenes con cáncer, Jonathan y Mark ayudan a un ex atleta adolescente con su ira y a un niño cuya madre es sobreprotectora.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan trata de que Miki, el negligente padre de Jason, se acerque un poco más a su hijo, pero él vive inmerso en su trabajo, evitando el dolor de la enfermedad del joven.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.sub-title: Bendice a los chicos de azul
programme.desc: Mark pide que Jonathan se convierta en policía. Su deseo es concedido, y Jonathan se convierte en humano para experimentar las difícultades que conlleva ese trabajo.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Una aspirante actriz busca ser aceptada por lo que realmente es. Jonathan la ayuda y convierte su historia en una versión moderna de Cenicienta.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan necesita la ayuda de un estafador para salvar a Mark, quien, engañado luego de un accidente, le vendió su alma al diablo.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan se muestra escéptico ante un actor que cree que vio a Dios sentado entre el público durante una función de teatro.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Mark ayuda a superar la tensa situación que está viviendo un amigo cuya hija adoptada busca a sus padres naturales.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan hace de cupido entre una solitaria mujer ciega y un escultor huraño, etiquetado como un monstruo por la gente del pueblo.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Julian es acusado de atacar a Rachel, quien está en coma. Jonathan y Scotty acuden a prestarle asistencia legal para demostrar su inocencia, y el joven abogado deberá demostrar de lo que es capaz.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan y Mark trabajan con un equipo de fútbol profesional, en donde descubren que la lesión de uno de los jugadores le ha provocado una dependencia a las drogas.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan y Mark ayudan a un abuelo, muy aficionado a los extraterrestres, a mantener la custodia legal sobre su nieto. Para ello, se hacen pasar por dos alienígenas.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Tanto Mark como Linda tienen opiniones negativas sobre el sexo opuesto. Por eso, piden intercambiar sus vidas y, cuando se les cumple el deseo, aprenden lo que es vivir en el cuerpo del otro.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: A Jonathan le toca una de las misiones más difíciles: volver a su antigua casa y ayudar a su viuda a recuperar las alegría de vivir.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan y Mark deben ayudar a un ángel mal aconsejado, que ha estado tratando de ganar sus alas durante 200 años.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan y Mark ayudan al padre de un soldado de Vietnam fallecido a honrar a su hijo en un servicio conmemorativo.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan y Mark ayudan a un anciano novelista a redescubrir su talento al reencontrarse y conectar con su nieto.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Un hogar para madres solteras está en riesgo, luego de que un reportero de TV acusa a la dirigente del lugar de malversación de fondos.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan y Mark animan a un niño con problemas mentales para competir en las Olimpiadas Especiales.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo
programme.desc: Jonathan y Mark ayudan a una joven pareja a adoptar un niño con problemas mentales.

programme.title: Autopista al cielo

programme.title: Horizontes De Sangre
programme.desc: Instigado por vendedores de armas el comanche lobo del desierto mata al jefe apache halcon veloz y hiere a su hijo pluma dorada, que es atendido por polvorilla, la osada esposa del teniente federal julian. los comanches arrasan el pueblo apache y pluma dorada y su gente se unen a la tropa del capitan roberto para luchar contra ellos. pluma dorada vence en duelo con hachas a lobo del desierto pero los aliados de este raptan a polvorilla, pues ojo de buitre la desea. los apaches y los federales los alcanzan y los derrotan.

programme.title: Son Tus Perjumenes Mujer
programme.desc: Espiridion pichinche, quien se caracteriza por su humildad y simpatia, trabaja como taquero, globero y cartero, ya que su sueno es llevar a alicia, su sobrina minusvalida, a un famoso parque de diversiones de estados unidos. mas tarde, pichinche se enamora de su vecina beatriz, una bella joven que aspira a ser actriz de television, asi que a cambio de los cuidados que tiene con su sobrina, el la ayuda a entrar a un centro de espectaculos, solo que las cosas no resultan como lo esperaban y ambos deben esforzarse mas para obtener lo que desean.

programme.title: Las Leandras
programme.desc: UN DIRECTOR TEATRAL USA UN ANTIGUO PROSTIBULO PARA SUS ENSAYOS Y LO HACE PASAR POR UN COLEGIO DE SENORITAS PARA QUE SU NOVIA PUEDA COBRAR UNA HERENCIA.

programme.title: Napoleoncito
programme.desc: NAPOLEON, EMPLEADO DE UN BANCO SUFRE LAS BURLAS DE SUS COMPANEROS POR SER UN HOMBRE CHAPARRO, SIN IMPORTARLE LAS BURLAS EL PRESUME DE CONQUISTAR A UNA FAMOSA ACTRIZ. SU JEFE LO RETA A PROBARLO A CAMBIO DE CONSTRUIR CONDOMINIOS EN LA VECINDAD DONDE VIVE NAPOLEON, QUE PASA GRANDES APUROS Y LLEGA A PAGAR A UN FORTACHON PARA QUE FINJA SER VENCIDO POR EL E IMPRESIONAR A LA ACTRIZ. POR UNA CONFUSION NAPOLEON DE VERDAD SALVA A LA ACTRIZ DE SER ROBADA POR UN GIGANTON Y EN AGRADECIMIENTO ELLA ACCEDE A MOSTRARSE COMO AMIGA DE EL. EL BANQUERO NI SE FIJA EN EL PERO NAPOLEON LO HACE RECAPACITAR CON UN DISCURSO SOBRE POBRES Y RICOS, CONSIGUIENDO SU ANHELADO CONDOMINIO Y POSTERIORMENTE SE DECLARA A UNA VECINA.

programme.title: La nortena de mis amores
programme.desc: CARLOS MACIAS, YA CONVERTIDO EN UN HOMBRE HECHO Y DERECHO DECIDE REGRESAR EL DIA DE SU CUMPLEANOS NUMERO 21 A SU PUEBLO NATAL, ESTO CON EL FIN DE COBRAR VENGANZA EN CONTRA DE JACINTO ESCOBEDO, UN HOMBRE AFICIONADO A LAS OPUESTAS QUE POR AMBICIOSO COMETIO EL CRIMEN DE MATAR A RAMON MACIAS, PADRE DE CARLOS DE UN DISPARO EN LA ESPALDA. APOYADO DE SU GENTE CARLOS ESTA DISPUESTO A LUCHAR EN CONTRA DE JACINTO Y HACERLO PAGAR POR SU CRIMEN, ASI MISMO APOYA A UNA MUJER CUYO PADRE TAMBIEN SE VE INVOLUCRADO EN EL MAL JUEGO DE JACINTO Y A QUIEN LE HA QUITADO TODAS SUS PERTENENCIAS COMO ALGUNA VEZ LO HIZO CON SU PADRE RAMON.

programme.title: Remolino De Pasiones
programme.desc: Gabriela es una mujer de cierta edad y de posicion acomodada cuya hija esta preparando su proximo enlace matrimonial. La tranquilidad queda dinamitada despues que Gabriela conozca a Alejandro, un joven que guarda un asombroso parecido al hombre que ella amo en su juventud. Lejos de echarse atras, Alejandro pretende sacar partido de esta circunstancia y se propone seducir a Gabriela. Esta decision a la larga se manifestara como funesta. Provocara que el matrimonio de la hija de Gabriela naufrague, que el marido de ella fallezca y la miseria moral los devore por completo.

programme.title: Caceria Humana
programme.desc: Dos adolescentes alberto y su novia lucy se escapan a la playa, el problema es que el padre de ella se opone a esta relacion por sus diferencias economicas, asi que los manda a buscar en su luna de miel, a la par, un hombre persigue a la pareja provocandoles un accidente automovilistico que les quita la vida. mas tarde, rodrigo, hermano de alberto, acude a identificar su cuerpo, alli se entera que no es el primer incidente que le ocurre a otras parejas, ademas, el mismo es victima de un atentado, situacion que le hace sospechar mas cuando conoce a olivia, una mujer que tambien perdio a su hermano en las mismas circunstancias, de este modo, ambos intentan descubrir la verdad detras de sus muertes pero a alberto le aguarda una terrible sorpresa.

programme.title: PUNTO DE CONTROL
programme.desc: Un alguacil y un vagabundo luchan contra una celula terrorista cuyo objetivo es aduenarse de los Estados Unidos.

programme.title: UNA NOVIA MUY ESPECIAL
programme.desc: Un hombre enamorado de una mujer judia le pide a un amigo judio un consejo sobre como actuar como un miembro de la comunidad.

programme.title: PERRO DE HOLLYWOOD
programme.desc: Una supercelebridad canina esta harta de que los ejecutivos de Hollywood lo traten mal. Decide escapar del estilo de vida de las grandes estrellas y encuentra a un grupo de ninos que lo cuidan.

programme.title: FEO DE DIA LINDO DE NOCHE
programme.desc: Lorenzo siempre sono con ser guapo y gracias a un conjuro su deseo se hizo realidad. Pronto descubrira que ser tan agraciado no es facil y justo en el momento que todo es una hermosura, una bella mujer se enamora de el, pero del lado feo.

programme.title: BARBARA
programme.desc: Barbara, un travesti fantasioso, es despedido del club nocturno en el cual trabaja. Como venganza, roba un valioso maletin y se escapa al llano, donde conoce a Sixto. Juntos inician un viaje mientras son perseguidos por el Polaco.

programme.title: ESTRATERRESTRES
programme.desc: Una Familia, 100.000 pollos con una sentencia de muerte, una chica con un secreto que revelar a toda su Familia y una estrella a 2.500 millones de anos luz de distancia que les hara comprender que todos estamos metaforicamente fuera de este mundo.

programme.title: JUSTIYCIA
programme.desc: Justino es un exminero que sobrevivio a un tragico accidente en el trabajo, en el que perecieron siete de sus companeros. Harto de la situacion social y economica que vive el pais, decide, impulsivamente, convertirse en un justiciero social.

programme.title: EL CAMINO CORRECTO
programme.desc: Arturo, un nino de la ciudad de El Verde Bonao en la Republica Dominicana rural, aprovecha las oportunidades que se le presentan yendo a la ciudad con la esperanza de ayudar a su madre, a la que acaban de diagnosticar leucemia. Todo cambia cuando menos lo esperaba.

programme.title: INSTRUCCIONES PARA LA POLIGAMIA
programme.desc: Fabiana esta dispuesta a cualquier cosa con tal de lograr su objetivo: ser madre. Incluso, a conspirar con una amiga, manipular a un hombre y pedirle esperma a un desconocido.

programme.title: JUANITA
programme.desc: Juanita regresa a su tierra natal en la Republica Dominicana para pasar la Navidad con su familia acompanada por Mariano, un agricultor espanol mucho mayor que ella. A su llegada, Juanita confiesa que tiene dos hijos y Mariano tambien descubre que ella ha permitido que Jairo, el padre de sus hijos, vive en su casa para ayudar con los hijos. A cambio, Mariano confiesa haberse aprovechado de su estatus ilegal para que se quede con el. En medio de estas confesiones, la avalancha de familiares y amigos cae sobre ellos.

programme.title: UMA
programme.desc: Uma, vive en Italia y conoce a un escritor. Hay una quimica inexplicable entre ambos, una historia de amor que surge en las maravillosas costas de Gaeta, hasta que cruzan la hermosa tierra de Florencia, donde un accidente cambiara sus vidas.

programme.title: UN AMOR DE PELICULA
programme.desc: Bernardo es un productor de cine cercano a la bancarrota que decide convencer erroneamente a un famoso director de cine de hacer una mala pelicula para poder ganar mucho dinero. Laura, su novia y agente, se convierte en su confidente y musa.

programme.title: Mostro Garage
programme.desc: Con Franky Mostro recorreremos todo el mundo del automovilismo, viajes increibles y resenas de autos

programme.title: Gastronomia
programme.desc: La influencer Mariana Kattab nos ensena recetas increibles y faciles de hacer

programme.title: Conecta

programme.title: Mi Ex Me Tiene Ganas
programme.desc: Pilar se desvanece en medio de su casamiento con Cornelio. Alonso se va al patio, superado por la situacion. Pilar vuelve en si y pide seguir con el casamiento. Cuando Pilar, Cornelio, Andrea, Dolores y Valentin regresan a la casa de Pilar para empacar las cosas, se encuentran con Talia. Ella dijo no haber ido al casamiento porque se sentia mal. Valentin y Dolores se ofrecen a quedarse con Andrea mientras Pilar realiza la mudanza a la casa de Cornelio. Ellos llegan a la casa de Cornelio, y mientras preparan todo para ir a pasar la noche a un hotel, gracias al regalo de Miranda, Pilar encuentra ropa interior de otra mujer, por lo que discute con Cornelio. Cornelio le miente y dice que la ropa interior es de una estriper contratada por sus amigos, y finalmente, parten hacia el hotel.

programme.title: Corazon Apasionado
programme.desc: Marcos, en su estado de locura, visita a Patricia bien tarde en la noche y es ahi cuando Armando tiene una pesadilla y siente que su amada esta en peligro. Cuando va a la casa a verla, como era de esperarse, Patricia no se deja ver. - Ursula convence a Mariana de que se quede viviendo con ella. Por mas de que esta ultima cree que trajo varias molestias, acepta hacerle compania a La Generala por mucho tiempo mas. Patricia sigue en su postura de no querer ver a Armando para que el no vea su cicatriz. Es por eso que cuando Armando se presenta en su cuarto para hablar con ella, Alvaro le prohibe entrar y se arma una pelea. Ambos se insultan y Patricia piensa que el culpable de todo es Armando ya que el provoco al doctor.

programme.title: ¿Vieja Yo?
programme.desc: Estefania le insinua a Justo que debe haber algun enemigo oculto que filtro la informacion sobre su ausencia del Caiman para crear el conflicto con Margot. Justo se queda pensando, tratando de decidir quien podria ser el enemigo. Los hombres del Caiman, incluyendo a Jose Antonio, debaten acerca del nefasto futuro que le espera a Justo cuando se enfrente a Margot. Don Pipo se suma al grupo y pregunta de que se trata la charla. Los muchachos dudan en decirle algo pensando en su reaccion al enterarse de la crisis entre Justo y Margot. Se lo dicen y todos rien. Por su parte, las mujeres se reunen en otro sector y tanto Rosalia como Tamara le sugieren a Ixora que se paso de la raya y que el riesgo de que la boten es bastante grande.

programme.title: Corazon Esmeralda
programme.desc: Juan Andres le cuenta a Jaime que Beatriz es la quinta heredera. Elia habla con su mama Hortensia sobre Luis David; su mama lo compara con su tio Domingo; Elia no le cree cuando dice que esta vivo y lo ve en la villa. Blanca se enfurece segura de que Rocio esta con Miguel y le pide a Silvestre que la ayude a buscarlos. Rocio duda de poder vivir bien con Miguel, sin trabajo y sin dinero. Blanca llega con furia al meson de Lucha, discute con Luisa y Ramon amenazandolos. Lorena le cuenta a Melinda que Rocio y Miguel escaparon juntos. Silvestre informa a Luisa y Ramon que Miguel efectivamente esta de novio con Rocio, Blanca amenaza con denunciar a Miguel con la policia, Ramon la amenaza con gritar en la plaza del pueblo la verdad sobre Beatriz.

programme.title: Morena Clara
programme.desc: Victor desesperado por ver a Maritza de la cual esta enamorado, pasa cerca de su casa y ve a Teresina la muchaca de servicio y le pide por favor que le entrege una carta a Maritza, ella por supuesto que se niega, pero luego el la convence y ella acepta. - Linda lleva a su nuevo apartamento a su amiga Katerina y ella se queda anonadada por lo bello que esta decorado, Linda paro su parte insoportable como siempre le dice a ella que ese sera el nido de amor de ella y Valentin.

programme.title: La Mujer de mi Vida
programme.desc: Tras su encuentro con Severo la policia efectua el arresto de Alexandra, esta resistiendose a ser encarcelada acusa a Barbarita como la culpable de la muerte de Larry. En el cementerio Barbarita se despide de Larry prometiendole siempre llevarlo en su recuerdo, Antonio Adolfo conversa con Barbarita demostrandose afectado por lo ocurrido a su enemigo y viendose rechazado nuevamente por Barbarita. En la carcel Gustavo conversa con Katiuska ofreciendole su apoyo para ayudarla a demostrar su inocencia. Renato y Lola se consuelan mutuamente llevando consigo el dolor por la muerte de Larry, Jessika los informa sobre la captura de Alexandra, Renato se hace la promesa de refundirla para siempre en la carcel.

programme.title: Lellobee City Farm
programme.sub-title: Reading / Going to the Hospital / Healthy Habits (montage) / Accidents Happen Play Time / Heads, Shoulders, Knees and Toes
programme.desc: Ella takes out a book from the street library, but Rishi is not too bothered. Ella shows him the amazing variety of stories that are available - he just has to find the one that's right for him. Rishi looks at books about cowboys, dragons, spaceships and fairy tales. He wants to hear all their stories! / Lettie, Carlos and Go-Go are unwell so a makeshift animal hospital is set up at the farm. Headaches, temperatures and coughs are all treated. Ella helps Sami the vet, and soon the animals are all feeling better. Well done Ella and Sami! / A song that highlights what habits everyone should do daily in order to lead a healthy life - brushing their teeth, washing their hands, eating healthy foods and exercising. 'If you want a good day, do everything the healthy way, healthy is the way to be, with your friends at Lellobee City Farm! / Ella, Rishi and Izzy are playing in the playground but Ella falls off the swing, Rishi crashes his scooter and Ben flies off the end of the slide. Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! Fortunately their parents and grandparents are there to pick them up, dust them off and send them on their way again. / It's animal bath time at the farm! With a fun twist on the traditional lyrics of 'Head and Shoulders, Knees and Toes', Ella and Rishi wash the "Mane, Muzzle, Back and Hooves" of Heidi the horse, Pablo the pig and Mama Duck. It's time to get scrubbing!

programme.title: Luna Chip & Inkie Adventure Rangers Go
programme.desc: It's a frogvasion! Eagle Creekers are finding frogs in vegetable bins at the General Store, under hats and even in their bathtubs! It looks like the citizens will have to move unless the Adventure Rangers can lure the little hoppers back to their home pond. But even dressing Chip up as a big, juicy mosquito doesn't draw the frogs away. Finally, the Rangers investigate why the frogs have moved and find that their pond is filled with litter! All they have to do is clean up that mess and everyone will be happy. Except for Chip, who is still dressed as that tasty mosquito.

programme.desc: Not Another Black Movie stars Damon Williams (Bad Boys of Comedy, Comic View, BET LIVE, The Tom Joyner Morning Show), Janet Hubert (The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air), Rodney Perry (The Monique Show, Who's Got Jokes) Jay Davis (Not Another Zombie Movie, Shots Fired), and Leon Rogers (WGCI, Comic View, Bad Boys of Comedy). - Not Another Black Movie is not only a spoof of a genre often associated with Tyler Perry films, but a satirical look at family dysfunction as well. Written by Jay Davis and Directed by Donte "Diesel" Williams, Not Another Black Movie addresses issues that effect many families whether they be rich or poor, black or white. Although we poke fun at some of the stereotypical roles portrayed in this genre, we hope to shed some light on problems that plague many families while giving you a good laugh.

The BMW 235i RS has a great rear wheel performance and the Porsche Cayman GTS with its mid-engine puts a smile on your face as soon as you put your foot on the accelerator.

programme.title: Supercars
programme.sub-title: AMG GT R - The Beast of The Green Hell
programme.desc: In this special, we followed the promotion shoot for the Mercedes-AMG GT R in Thailand and at the famous Nurburgring Nordschleife race track, where Formula One world champion Lewis Hamilton showed why this super car bears the nickname "The Beast of the Green Hell".

programme.title: Supercars
programme.desc: How do you top the already in many ways superior iconic Porsche 911? - You come up with the GT3. - The Porsche 911 GT3 with its 475 hp engine is the ultimate melange of road suitability and race track compatibility. And the German brand's RS model is even more intense when it comes to power, performance and ultimate sports car feel.

programme.title: Supercars
programme.desc: What has been known in motorsports for ages is now used for road vehicles as well: lightweight construction. In many cases the magic word is carbon. The German manufacturer Roding created a car that even outshined the Porsche GT3 with an impressive power/weight ratio. British makes like the Caterham 620 R, Lotus Elise or Radical RXC also showed what's in play in regards to lightweight sports cars.

programme.title: Mercedes-AMG GT S Performmaster
programme.desc: Not far from Stuttgart is the home of the tuner Performmaster who specialize in the performance optimization of Mercedes-AMG models. They turned the already more-than-potent GT S sports car into a beast.

programme.title: Porsche Cayman GT4
programme.desc: The Porsche Cayman GT4. Lighter, more powerful and faster than ever. Porsche shows what is possible with this vehicle, when fast lap times are in the focus of attention.

programme.title: Dreamcars
programme.desc: British coupes are instant classics and just as cool as James Bond. Aston Martin, Bentley and Jaguar produce the most exclusive and elegant coupes in the world. Their distinctive design is still inspired by the iconic Jaguar E-Type and Aston Martin DB5.

programme.title: Maserati Gran Turismo Coupe Stradale
programme.desc: Risk-taking and precision is what a poker player needs to have. What does this have to do with the Maserati Gran Turismo Coupe Stradale? It combines both characteristics in an amazing way.

programme.title: Dreamcars
programme.desc: With their avantgarde design, superior technology and driving pleasure, German coupes like the Porsche 911, the Mercedes S-Class Coupe, the BMW 6-series or the Audi RS5 embody the passion for driving.

programme.title: Dreamcars
programme.desc: They are the embodiment of a sportscar, the coupes by Ferrari, Lamborghini, Maserati and Alfa Romeo are breathtaking and irrisistible. Created by the most famous designers in the world, every Italian sportscar is a piece of art.

programme.title: Dreamcars
programme.desc: With their extraordinary design and powerful engines, international coupes by Maserati, Porsche, Bentley, Mercedes and Rolls Royce evoke more emotions than any other car. They are the epitome of elegance and exclusivity.

programme.title: Volvo Laplander 6x6

programme.sub-title: SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 16, Mexico World Finals (Part 2)

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 1, Norway - World Strongest Viking
programme.desc: Season 2018 begins with 14 strongest men in the world, all competing for the title. The competition kicks off in Norway. We’ll see typical Viking disciplines, team events and world records in heavy conditions in the land of snow and ice. They will suffer, they will freeze and fight in this first competition of the year for the title that they will carry on their shoulders throughout whole year.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 2, Germany - FIBO Power
programme.desc: The next stop in strongest league of the world is muscle capital, largest number of strong shoulders per capichampions league on the planet. It’s a FIBO - the biggest expo on planet Earth and the second stage of 2018 Strongman champions league, in Cologne, Germany.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: For the first time in history, Strongman Champions League will set up competition in Abu Dhabi. The line-up of super athletes, who are part of the SCL, includes former world champions Dainis Zageris (Latvia) & Krzysztof Radzikowski (Poland), current world champion Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia) and biggest strongman in the World Sean O’Hagan (Ireland).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: Strongman classic in land where there is no place for anything else excepts strength, fight and endurance. Here are fourteen of the strongest men, fighting for the title of strongest in Holland.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: We go back to Holland, where former champion Dainis Zageris is in leading position after the first three events. Alongside Radzikowski, he is in this moment favorite for world title, and also leader shirt holder.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: Stage six of Strongman champions league, 2018 is set back on north, in Finland. Here we have Matjaz Belsak, wearing SCL leader shirt, one of the biggest strongman in the World Mika Torro, fan favorite strongman in all over the World – Will Baggott, and also big name from Baltic – Aivars Smaukstelis

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: Twelve strongman, including defending Worldchampion Matjaz Belsak from Slovenia , will compete on “Air spa” for the title of best in homeland country of Tesla, Pupin, Novak Djokovic. Matjaz Belsak is the SCL leader in this competition, chasing his third victory this season.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: The World championship in lightweights of the Strongman Champions League bring to us 50 strongmen from all over the world. All athletes are under 105 kilograms and for them this is the step up to the ultimate heavyweights.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: In this second stage of the World championship of lightweights we will find out who out of the 12 athletes will win the title in the under 105 kilogram category.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: The first part of SCL Romania 2018 will be hosted in Brasov. This episode features a new event for Strongman Champion League: “ The Chopper Pull”!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: After three classical Strongman events – Dead lift, Loading and Front hold – and one historical, Chopper Pull for the first time in history of Strongman, now we go to find out who will take title in Romania. This is the second stage in Romania and it remains to be seen who will win the title; Aivars, Travis or Krzyzstof?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: This is it the last show before the world final. These guys have really got to fight for the points now, this is going to be action packed, whilst these guys fight it out all day.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: The next destination of Strongman Champions League is in a piece of paradise on earth – Curacao. We bring to you some special Strongman events like the Rock Lift, Tug of War and Weight for Height in this episode.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: This is the last competition before the grand finals. After the first three events Zageris is in top place, but can O’Hagan, Baggott, Petursson and Ortmayer step into the final? Last chance some of them will find through events like Forward Hold, Truck Pull, Dead Lift and loading very big objects.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 14, Road to Mexico
programme.desc: We bring you 50 minutes of Strongman inside. Fears, inspiration, courage, the best and worst from our finalists and their expectation of the finals. We also go to Poland and Germany to represent one day in the training of Krzysztof Radzikowski and Dennis Kohlruss. See all the finalists for Mexico in their comfort zone here, with their backgrounds /motivations /family and friends.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 15, Mexico - World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first part of the Strongman Champions League 2018 finals in Mexico. The last twelve athletes all pushing their boundaries and testing their limits to take the World title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 16, Mexico - World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: After 11 months and 14 competitions all over the world, it all comes down to the final in this episode. The strongmen must show their best skills and every mistake is expensive, so their concentration must be at the highest possible level. Will Krzysztof manage to take off back or will Dainis maintain his lead?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 1, World Strongest Viking
programme.desc: This year 14 athletes from all over the world came to Fefor to compete in 6 cruel events. programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: The next stop in strongest league of the world is muscle capital, largest number of strong shoulders per capita in the World and of course, the most powerful host in Strongman champions league on the planet. programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: On a spectacular beach in Alanya, the MLO Strongman Champions League Turkey was viewed by thousands of spectators over a two day battle. With 12 athletes at the start over 6 cruel events, like Marble Stone Lift, Truckpull and Deadlift cars. And with the comeback of Travis Ortmayer / USA, former stone king and world ranked competitor. Winner of several SCL stages in the past.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: Four times Strongest Man of Holland, Alex Moonen and the “Flying Dutchman” Kelvin de Ruiter competing here in Holland against 12 other strongest men in the world. There were 6 events in total, and 3 in this episode: The first event, a truckpull of 17.000 kg over 25 meters in max 75 seconds, was a real hard pull Also for the World Champion Truckpull, Holland’s runner-up Kelvin de Ruiter, but watch his amazing technique here.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: Strongest Man of Holland, Alex Moonen and the “Flying Dutchman” Kelvin de Ruiter, competing in Holland against 12 other strongest men in the world. There were 6 events in total, 3 in this second episode; a Viking-press of 150 kg with the current world record holder Luke Herrick. The fifth event, a front hold of 25 kg is loved or hated by the athletes and lastly, the Stones of Strength.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.desc: An unbelievable TANK PULL of 50.000 kg was at the stage of SCL RUSSIA. Never seen this before! Not only a tank pull was done here but also the Viking Press/ Deadlift Max and Log lift reps were spectacular events to see here in Russia. With Mikhail Koklyaev also as event presenter, the former top 3 world strongest man from Russia was there

A DOCUMENTARY+ Original film.

programme.title: Kid Yamaka
programme.desc: In this deeply human story, Emmy-nominated director Matt Ogens explores boxer Zachary "Kid Yamaka” Wohlman’s difficult past, his training under world-class coach Freddie Roach, and his path to personal redemption through boxing, Judaism, and sobriety. With Zachary’s 2021 passing, this film serves as a moving tribute to his hustle, heart and soul and to all those who struggle with addiction.

programme.title: Nuts!
programme.desc: Meet Dr. John Romulus Brinkley, an eccentric genius who built an empire in Depression-era America with a goat testicle impotence cure and a million watt radio station. This Sundance award-winner from director Penny Lane uses animated reenactments, interviews, archival footage, and a hilariously unreliable narrator to trace Brinkley’s rise from poverty and obscurity to the heights of celebrity, wealth and influence in Depression-era America.

programme.title: Stealing Rodin
programme.desc: Stealing Rodin tells the unforgettable story of the greatest art theft in Chile's history. In 2005, the Palace of Fine Arts in Santiago, hosted a collection by celebrated French sculptor Auguste Rodin. The morning after the exhibit’s opening, museum guards were dismayed to find that one of the Rodin pieces had gone missing. The "theft" turned out to be a provocative statement, masterminded by a precocious art student. His actions sparked a public outcry and a furious debate on the nature of art itself.

programme.title: Chrysler C-300

programme.title: Ponga su carro en la TV

programme.title: Ponga su carro en la TV

programme.title: Ponga su carro en la TV

programme.title: BMW M6 Gran Coupé
programme.desc: El M6 Gran Coupé es la última joya de las plantas M de BMW. Es ancho y bajo y cuenta con las tomas de aire extragrandes típicas de esta serie. Los bávaros sacan a relucir su martillo V8 y demuestran lo que significa tener la sensación de volar.

programme.title: Porsche 911 GT3 RS
programme.desc: Los grandes alerones traseros sugieren que hay mucha potencia escondida bajo el capó que debe ser controlada, ya que estos alerones proporcionan la carga aerodinámica necesaria. El Porsche GT3 RS tiene un alerón trasero muy especial.

programme.title: Supercoches
programme.desc: Hay marcas que suenan como música celestial para los amantes de los coches: el Mc Laren MP4 12C, el Porsche 911 Turbo S y el Mercedes SLS AMG GT son superdeportivos que no tienen parangón. Pisamos el acelerador a fondo de estos fascinantes y potentes vehículos.

programme.title: Supercoches
programme.desc: 1.000 kilómetros en el famoso Nürburgring. Es la última carrera de la temporada 2013. Echamos un vistazo a todo lo relacionado con la acción, los pilotos, sus coches y la carrera.

programme.title: Supercoches
programme.desc: Porsche presentó su Panamera 4 S con un motor biturbo de 6 cilindros en lugar de un V8 de succión natural que ofrecía menor desplazamiento, más potencia y menor consumo de combustible. Y además: Jaguar se reinventó a sí mismo con el XJ, ofreciendo tecnología moderna con un diseño de moda; el Modelo S de Tesla es el primer sedán de lujo totalmente eléctrico.

programme.title: Supercoches
programme.desc: Alfa Romeo y Rolls Royce, dos marcas que no parecen tener muchas similitudes pero que son legendarias para los entusiastas de los coches. programme.title: Ford GT40
programme.desc: Con sus coches V8, los estadounidenses demostraron a finales de los años 60 que también podían construir coches ganadores. El Ford GT 40 es uno de estos coches. Al principio, el proyecto "Victory at Le Mans" de Ford USA amenazaba con fracasar.

programme.title: Historia carro
programme.desc: Desde el principio, AMG se ha fijado el objetivo de representar las máximas prestaciones automovilísticas, la exclusividad y el placer de conducción dinámico. Ya sea en el deporte del motor o en la carretera, AMG lleva más de 50 años marcando pautas.

programme.title: Historia carro
programme.desc: Vehículos excepcionales y éxitos legendarios en el mundo del motor por un lado, golpes del destino y errores económicos por el otro. Pero el mito de Lancia sigue vivo.

programme.title: Historia carro
programme.desc: Son elegantes, extravagantes y suecos: los coches de la marca de culto Saab. Desde el principio, Saab construyó coches diferentes: carrocerías individuales, tecnología innovadora, seguridad ejemplar. Mostramos el ascenso y la caída de la empresa.

programme.title: Historia carro

programme.desc: In this final practice we allow for more spaciousness, so give yourself ample time for the 30-minute practice and at least 5 minutes of journaling afterward. programme.title: Deep Relaxation with Tracee Stanley
programme.desc: Move beyond the mind and connect with a deeper part of yourself. Experiment and let go and explore your true nature to create a new way of being in the world.

programme.title: Good Mood Food with Jason Wrobel
programme.desc: On our last day of the course together, Jason will show you specific mindfulness practices for enhancing your emotional health, discuss how meditation affects neuroplasticity, and teach you how to balance your neurotransmitters and the hemispheres of the brain.

programme.title: Deep Relaxation with Tracee Stanley
programme.desc: This class focuses on becoming aware of all parts of the physical body and inviting them to relax. Known as “systematic relaxation,” this practice allows you to create a new relationship with your physical body and deepen your ability to move into “rest and digest.”

programme.title: Good Mood Food with Jason Wrobel
programme.desc: It’s time to unleash your inner MasterChef today! Jason discusses his mindset and ethos around making a meal, including principles for balancing flavors, textures, mouthfeel.

programme.title: Good Mood Food with Jason Wrobel
programme.desc: Today is all about feeling hangry, when you get so hungry, you actually get angry! Jason shares the hormones that affect hanger and how you can be mindful of controlling them. We’ll discuss the importance of proper hydration, blood sugar levels, starvation diets, and weight loss.

programme.title: Yoga For All
programme.desc: Your Day 2 session invites you to use the tools of the at-home yoga practice to befriend your body and your breath. Build on the art of noticing from Day 1 as we expand our vocabulary with a focus on a strong foundation. This session encourages a healthy flow of energy up and down the spine and lovingly guides you to learn how to take responsibility for your experience on the mat.

programme.title: Yoga For All
programme.desc: Your day 3 practice invites you to get to know your body through the structure of the practice and the art of aligning. We build on day 1 and 2 with a focus on action and alignment through asana and energy.

programme.title: Yoga For All
programme.desc: Your Day 4 practice provides you the opportunity to lean in when you feel discomfort to embrace the process of finding ease. Discover layers of your home practice as we look at our patterns and continue to build a dynamic vocabulary that serves.

programme.title: The Nature of Reality
programme.sub-title: The Nature of Reality: The Science of Reality
programme.desc: What is real? How do we know it's real, and how does that deeper understanding of reality help us fulfill our dreams, desires, and intentions? So let's go for it.

programme.title: The Nature of Reality
programme.sub-title: The Nature of Reality: Fundamental Experience
programme.desc: Let's shift away from the scientific model to a different way of looking at that which we call reality.

programme.title: Live Fearlessly with Anita Moorjani
programme.sub-title: Guided Meditation to Move Forward & Release Fear
programme.desc: Today’s meditation will guide you through forgiveness. Of letting go of obstacles and fears that hold you back from living the life you desire to live. By doing so, you’ll be able to forgive everyone who has hurt you in this life, release emotional baggage that may be weighing heavy on you, and step into a new realm of possibility.

programme.title: Live Fearlessly with Anita Moorjani
programme.sub-title: How to Transcend Fear into Love
programme.desc: We live in a fear-based world. In today’s lesson, Anita offers you tools that have been specially created to overcome your fears with love. This is the greatest lesson she learned during her near-death experience when she traveled to the other side. It’s the lesson that saved her life.

programme.title: Meditations for Manifestation
programme.desc: Join Kino for a 20 minute meditation on love and tuning into the flow of love in personal relationships.

programme.title: Meditations for Manifestation
programme.desc: Start your meditation practice with a few moments of mindful awareness built around the movement of the breath and the sensations of the body.

programme.title: The Work of Byron Katie
programme.desc: The way you recall a memory and the way it actually happened might be completely different. The question is, do you know which version feeds you? We can become so wrapped up in our recollections, we convince ourselves of these untruths. Is that person a monster? Were they wishing you harm? Or were they dealing with a difficult situation in the best way they knew how?

programme.title: The Work of Byron Katie
programme.sub-title: My Husband Doesn't Want Me as a Business Partner
programme.desc: Fear is a fickle partner. While it certainly serves a purpose — keeping us out of danger and forcing us to question our assumptions — if we give too much of ourselves over to fear, it will lead us down paths filled with insecurity, broken social interactions, and a persistent struggle against the way things actually are.

programme.title: Healing Conversations
programme.desc: If you want to step into healing conversations, you have to have a clear understanding of where you’re going, and it starts within: the first healing conversation you need to have is with yourself.

programme.title: Healing Conversations
programme.desc: This session is an insight session that is designed to follow the previous lesson (so go back if you haven’t watched it yet). You’ll integrate everything you’ve learned so far and set yourself up for taking practical action in your life. By doing this work, you’ll step more fully into your vision for your life and your vision for the world.

programme.title: Ayurvedic Nutrition
programme.desc: What is the Ayurvedic understanding of the mind-gut connection? In this segment, we cover the way our body works in harmony with the world around us.

programme.title: Ayurvedic Nutrition
programme.desc: What does it mean to experience symptoms of imbalance? In this segment we review what’s happening in your body and how you can use food to bring it back to balance. We start with vata.

programme.title: Abundant Joy with Scott Schwenk
programme.desc: Welcome to Abundant Joy! Remember, love isn't given or taken. It's an expression of the great Self, the one consciousness that animates all life.

programme.title: Ayurvedic Nutrition
programme.desc: Ayurveda relies upon the intelligence of the cosmos–if you want to understand how the universe works, you must tune in to your own cycles. In this course, you’ll learn how to use the principles of Ayurveda to bring the focus back to you so you can make more intuitive and informed health decisions.

programme.title: Ayurvedic Nutrition
programme.desc: The universe and everything in it was created with five elements: earth, water, fire, wind, and ether. For the creation of the planet, five elements came together in different proportions, and since we are made of the five elements, it takes these five elements to feed and nourish us. Once we understand our composition, and how these elements work in our body, we can start to understand what we need to replenish ourselves.

programme.title: Ayurvedic Nutrition

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Violet has a treasure chest, inside which Luna-Loo likes the moon stone the most. That day, Luna-Loo hides the treasure chest somewhere else without Violet’s permission, but what she doesn’t know is that Ms. Lady Jane witnesses the whole thing. The cubs are busy helping Violet look for the chest, while Luna-Loo is invited to Ms. Lady Jane’s office, where she hears Violet’s words about how she cherishes the chest. Luna-Loo realizes what she has done is not right. Ms. Lady Jane comes in. She asks Luna-Loo to return a screwdriver to Vick, and tells her that even though she likes the screwdriver, she can’t keep it because she’s not the owner. Luna-Loo puts the chest back and makes a confession to her friends.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.sub-title: The Family Visit & You Get What You Put In
programme.desc: Little Briar misbehaves at kindergarten and refuses to apologize to the other kids. Ms. Olivia happens to go to the kids’ home for family visits. Briar is afraid that mom will learn about his behavior at kindergarten, so he tries various means to stop the family visit. Despite of this, Ms. Olivia still meets Briar’s mom. Seeing he could do nothing to stop the family visit, Briar tells the truth. Ms. Olivia tells Briar that he needs to confront his problems, and Briar learns a valuable lesson.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.sub-title: Tiki the Weatherman & Herby’s Helpful Apples
programme.desc: Old Billy forecasts the weather right, and Tiki asks Old Billy to teach him how to forecast a rainy day. Tiki makes notes and memorizes it. The other kids at Pine Tree Kindergarten plan to have a picnic, and Tiki tells them the weather will be sunny. However, just when the kids are going to have the picnic, it rains. Tiki goes to find Old Billy and asks him what’s wrong with the weather forecast. Old Billy explains that nature changes constantly and that only by studying hard could they make weather forecasts as accurate as possible.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.sub-title: Kitty the Tiger & The Magic Words
programme.desc: An uninvited guest, Kitty the tiger, sneaks into the drawing class, and shocks the whole class. But later this adorable tiger wins everybody’s heart. They like her, and volunteer to look after her. Kitty makes much trouble. However to make her happy, Prince Tiki lets her have his favorite bag. During naptime, kitty misses her mom so much that she can’t stop crying. Then the kids sing for her to help her sleep. It’s time to say goodbye. Everybody feels sad to part with her. Ms. Olivia promises that Kitty will attend the kindergarten when she grows up, making them happy again.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: Fierce begs Guardian to teach him martial arts, and Guardian lies to him that the secret of success is smile. Fierce takes his words seriously and keeps smiling all day, which scares his companions away. The martial arts competition kicks off on the next day. Fierce jumps onto the arena first and Poppy follows to take up the challenge. Just as the master predicted, Poppy knocks out Fierce with the slightest effort.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: Guardian keeps bragging about his glorious past and Fierce gets tired of his jawing away. Fierce plucks some wild fruits from a tree to eat, which makes him suffer from diarrhea. They take a short break and continue the journey. Several hours later, Fierce finds that he has passed the same fruit tree he met just now for three times and they are walking around in a circle. But Guardian doesn’t listen to him and moves on.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: Fierce and Guardian thank Cloud Hand for his delicious food and prepare to start off. Cloud Hand tells them they can stay overnight at his house because there are many bumpy roads nearby and they may get lost easily. Guardian refuses his invitation politely and draws Fierce away. But soon after, they cannot find their way and come back again. Cloud Hand makes up a guest room for them and says he’ll show them the way out of the forest the next morning.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: Cloud Hand is hung upside down on a tree with his feet tied. The branch breaks off and he drops onto the ground. Guardian says Cloud Hand must have been sleepwalking at night and tied himself to the tree. Cloud Hand falls for what he says and doesn’t feel angry at all. Guardian says the pig must have pretended to be so nice and they need to test his character. They throw a coin, an ingot of silver, and an ingot of gold onto the ground on purpose, only to find that Cloud Hand is not interested in them at all and just cares about his food materials. They put off their doubts completely and begin to enjoy the dishes Cloud Hand cooks.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: The cubs break the trophy they won at the sports meeting. Fear of being criticized by Ms. Oliva, they make up a story that a blue bird attacks Briar and accidentally breaks the trophy. Ms. Olivia sees through their lie and gives them a lesson on honesty. The cubs confess their fault, and fix the trophy together.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Bramble decides to keep the caterpillar he finds on his head, and see how it grows up and becomes a butterfly. As time goes by, the caterpillar becomes a pupa, and soon it will turn into a butterfly. But in the process of metamorphosis, Bramble worries that it might get stuck, and tries to help. Ms. Olivia stops him and tells him that it needs to do it itself to get enough strength to fly. Just as they expected, the butterfly finally comes out, dries its wings, and flies.

programme.title: Pondemonium

programme.desc: Joe Croaker finds himself a treat of a large lollipop. After gorging on it, Joe places the hollowed lollipop around his neck and starts to toy with it. Not until he tries in vain to remove the lolly does he realize that he is stuck in it. As the lolly around Joe’s neck begins to melt, it becomes sticky and attracts many leaves to it. Joe looks just like a scary monster in that leafy lollipop! The other bug buddies are all frightened at the sight of Joe, mistaking him for the ruthless monster that has swallowed Joe alive. To revenge their good friend, the folks conceive a plan to capture “the monster”. Joe is cornered into a big ditch, where the lollipop around his neck is broken apart by McBroom’s dung ball. Not until then do the folks realize that the “monster” is none other than Joe Croaker! Just when the frog is about to fly off the handle, his buddies have already made themselves scarce.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Joe Croaker is intrigued when he sees Niddy travels with her silk. The frog believes he might be able to do the same.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.sub-title: Joe's got a Fish Bone in His Throat
programme.desc: Joe Croaker is on the prowl for food and the fish obtained by Cosmo makes his mouth water. As is typical of Joe Croaker the greedy bully frog, he snatches the fish from Cosmo and quickly swallows it whole. But such voracity only results in the bones being stuck in Joe’s throat. Seeing Joe in great pain, Cosmo is in panic and at a loss what to do to help. At that moment, Bartle Bee happens to pass by and offers Joe his nectar to help ease the pain. But it fails to work. Then Bartle suggests two possible solutions he learnt from books, which are ramming down the bones with a bun and dissolving them with vinegar. Cosmo and Joe hurry to the Garbage can and score both a bun and a bottle of vinegar, but it turns out neither way helps remove the bones from Joe’s throat. In the end, proposed again by the resourceful Bartle Bee, they hang Joe Croaker upside down and succeed in swinging the bones out of Joe’s throat.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Fed up living in his shabby can house, Cosmo decides to find himself a sleek, cozy new place. First he is taken with the fancy-looking paper box with pretty patterns and good light, but Bartle Bee reminds him of its vulnerability to rain in wet seasons. So he keeps on searching his dream home. Then, a crystal clear glass jar commands Cosmo’s attention. Just when he is about to make it his new abode, the mole cricket’s warning against this heat-accumulating material discourages him from settling down there. So Cosmo has to look for other alternatives. Then he discovers a large magnet which he uses to attract pieces of parts together and make them into a solidly constructed iron house. After a long day’s rushing about, Cosmo retires to rest at his pleasant new home. But something bad happens. A coin is drawn to the magnet house and blocks the exit. Trapped inside his own house, Cosmo shouts for help, which invites Joe Croaker over. The frog agrees to help him out on the condition that Cosmo offers him both service and food. But instead of getting Cosmo out, Joe accidentally sets a large iron lid running, which crashes into the magnet house. Luckily enough, Cosmo is able to survive with the help of the mole cricket. In the end, Joe Croaker has to compensate Cosmo by offering him his service instead.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Cosmo has got a nice ice cream postage stamp, which is overheard by Joe Croaker. The thought of the tasty ice cream tempts the amphibian into a plot to steal the stamp from Cosmo. He tails Cosmo, and tries in vain to grab the stamp. Tired from the flight, Cosmo rests himself upon a branch, covering himself with the stamp. Seeing this as a good opportunity, Joe employs every possible method known to him to try to score the stamp. But none of them really works. Then the green vines hanging down the tree inspire him. He uses the vines to climb up and reaches out for the stamp. He then falls off onto the ground along with the stamp. Just when Joe assumes he has secured the ice cream stamp for good, a gust of wind blows it up to the tree again. Cosmo wakes up and joyfully takes the stamp back home.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.desc: Briar and Tiki chases their kite to Old Billy’s vegetable patch, and accidentally trample the vegetables. Although they try to correct the deed, but it just get worse. They try to avoid Old Billy in school and hesitate to apologize to him, for fear Old Billy will be angry. Briar tries to get Tiki and apologize to Old Billy. The old man tells them he’s going to the vegetable field to grow new vegetables. Briar and Tiki help him out. At last, they tell Old Billy the truth. The old man doesn’t get angry. Instead, he thinks they are responsible kids.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac

When she visits Violet’s home, however, she finds out her friends treasure her toys very much, and remembers the good times she has spent with her toys. Then it rains. Luna-Loo quickly goes outside to find her toys with Violet but can’t find them. She’s feels regret. The next morning, she’s surprised to find out that all her toys are back. It turns out her mom picks up those toys, cleans and mends them. Luna-Loo realizes her mistake and thanks her mom. Violet and Vick come to Luna-Loo’s home and help her modify some old toys. Everyone is happy.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.sub-title: Summoning the Sun & The Frog Friends

They are disappointed to find out the sun has already set. They decide to summon the sun. First they to use some “magic spells”, then an ice cream to “entice” the sun to come out. They even mimic the sound of roosters to try to call for the sun. The sun never comes out. Instead, Violet’s parents are woken by the noise. Through a little experiment, they explain to the kids about solar rotation and the switch of night and day.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac

They try to collect some fresh clean air from a flower field with bottles, and bring the air to the office. However, it’s hard to tell whether the fragrance is really inside the bottles. So they decide to use balloons to collect the scent. However, a little hedgehog accidentally pops the balloons when he tries to help them. Old Billy sees them and tells them that the stinky smell will go away if they keep good ventilation in the office.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Briar has a toothache and Vick tells him there are bugs eating his teeth, making him anxious. To get the bugs out, they try many methods, such as gargling water, asking Hoo Hoo to peck the bugs out, and singing to lure the bugs out, all of which are proven to be useless. At last, they go to see Nurse Beakman, then they find out the cause of tooth decay, and learn how to protect their teeth.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Violet has a treasure chest, inside which Luna-Loo likes the moon stone the most. The cubs are busy helping Violet look for the chest, while Luna-Loo is invited to Ms. Lady Jane’s office, where she hears Violet’s words about how she cherishes the chest. Luna-Loo realizes what she has done is not right. Ms. Lady Jane comes in. She asks Luna-Loo to return a screwdriver to Vick, and tells her that even though she likes the screwdriver, she can’t keep it because she’s not the owner. Luna-Loo puts the chest back and makes a confession to her friends.

Seeing he could do nothing to stop the family visit, Briar tells the truth. Ms. Olivia tells Briar that he needs to confront his problems, and Briar learns a valuable lesson.

Tiki goes to find Old Billy and asks him what’s wrong with the weather forecast. Old Billy explains that nature changes constantly and that only by studying hard could they make weather forecasts as accurate as possible.

During naptime, kitty misses her mom so much that she can’t stop crying. Then the kids sing for her to help her sleep. It’s time to say goodbye. Everybody feels sad to part with her. Ms. Olivia promises that Kitty will attend the kindergarten when she grows up, making them happy again.

Fierce jumps onto the arena first and Poppy follows to take up the challenge. Just as the master predicted, Poppy knocks out Fierce with the slightest effort.

He forgets his lines, and can’t act. Babu thinks he didn’t practice enough but Luna-Loo thinks he has stage fright. He gives his role to Ernie Jo. Then Babu’s dad helps him to overcome his stage fright, and asks him to imagine the audience as fruits. At last, Babu doesn’t feel nervous anymore and acts well in the show.

programme.desc: Violet invites her friends to her home, and has made proper arrangement. She thinks things will go smoothly. The Kitchen God takes over the edict with reverence and awe and follows them onto a mass of cloud heading for the Heaven. They look down at the village on the way and find the masses offering sacrifice to the Kitchen God, praying for happiness and good fortune.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve

He poses a “V” (stands for victory) gesture with Aquila in front of the palace and asks Sonar to draw a portrait of them to mark the occasion. Shortly after, a lowly clerk comes over and brings the Kitchen God into the palace.

Meanwhile, Rascal the rat finds the royal edict in the Kitchen God’s house and considers it a good opportunity to change the destinies of his family and himself. Rascal hides the edict to keep other animals from seeing it while the Kitchen God sees through his ruse and tries to recapture the edict. They get into an argument and start to scramble for the edict. Just then, Aquila and Sonar break into the house and join the scramble for the royal edict immediately. In the midst of chaos, the royal edict drops into a censer and is burned into ashes.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: The Kitchen God, Rascal, and the two watchmen stand helplessly in front of the censer. Suddenly, a beam of golden light comes from the hearth and the royal edict floats up to the sky. The edict is made public and the news about the upcoming guardian tournament spreads like wildfire. The Kitchen God feels very remorseful for not keeping the secret. However, Aquila says that in that case they don’t need to worry about where to look for the competitors because all the masters will gather at Mount Tai from every corner of the village at that time.

Ms. Olivia then encourages little Briar to play with the others. At last, the kids at the kindergarten have a good time listening to Vick telling stories of the outside world.

By utilizing this principle, they encourage the little guy to light up at last.
